

Please use Keep/Favorite/Archive and Junk tags on your weapons and armor.


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TMMania's Master Filter: One-Stop-Shop command for cleaning your vault, highlights your trash. 

This filter will keep/ignore:
- Tagged: Keep / Favorite / Archive [Please Use Tags]
- Highest LL Items
- All Exotics (Weapons and Armor) 
- Loadout Items
- Titan: 18+ Recovery
- Hunter: 18+ mobility and 13+ recovery  or 18+ Recovery 
- Warlock: 18+ Discipline and 17+ recovery
- All armor with 63+ stat rolls
- 15/20 Stat Pair w/ MW
- Triple 15 Stat Set w/ MW 
- Equal Stat Distribution
- 1 of every class item

Weapons:
- Highlights Sunset Items that are not masterworked, use the Keep / Favorite / Archive tags to ignore these items
- Pinnacles, Rituals and all MW'ed weapons that are sunset will be ignored.
- Using the Junk tag on weapons will result in them being highlighted.

You can specify the minimum stat roll for each class type in the last section of the rows with is:titan is:warlock, I have it set to 63 for all, I set it to 65 for my main and 63 for alt characters. Please use Keep/Favorite/Archive and Junk Tags
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


15/20 Pair: Armor that has 20 in one stat and 15 in another.

15 Triple: Armor that has 15 in 3 separate stats

Full House: Armor with an equal stat split'

New Weapon Sorting: For looking at weapons that you haven't inspected yet, this does require you to never click them in DIM, if you do click on a weapon, mark it junk if  you don't want it

 
